## LOGO ASSET REQUIREMENTS

### Where to Obtain Logos

**Official Press Kits (Preferred):**
1. **NY Post**: nypost.com/press-kit or contact press@nypost.com
2. **CNN**: cnn.com/press-room or mediacenter.cnn.com
3. **Washington Post**: washingtonpost.com/pr
4. **Becker's Spine**: beckershealthcare.com/contact
