# Google AI Studio Prompt: Fix Credentials Layout - All Horizontal in One Row

## OBJECTIVE
Fix the credentials badges layout so that ALL 5 badges appear in a single horizontal row across the page, with NO badges appearing underneath. Currently, the "Academic Faculty" badge is appearing on a second row below the other four badges, which needs to be corrected.

---

## PROBLEM IDENTIFIED

**Current Layout (INCORRECT):**
```
[Castle Connolly] [Dual Fellowship] [Board Certified] [Alpha Omega Alpha]
                    [Academic Faculty]
                         ↑
                    (appearing below)
```

**Desired Layout (CORRECT):**
```
[Castle Connolly] [Dual Fellowship] [Board Certified] [Alpha Omega Alpha] [Academic Faculty]
                              (all in one row)
```

---

## SOLUTION: CSS FIXES

### Option 1: Force 5-Column Grid (Recommended)

Replace the existing grid CSS with this:

```css
/* Credentials Grid - Fixed 5 Columns */
.credentials-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); /* Force exactly 5 equal columns */
  gap: 24px;
  margin-top: 40px;
  max-width: 1400px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
}

/* Remove the auto-fit that was causing wrapping */
/* OLD CODE (DELETE THIS):
.credentials-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr)); ← This caused wrapping
  gap: 32px;
}
*/
```

---

### Option 2: Flexbox Single Row (Alternative)

If you prefer flexbox instead of grid:

```css
/* Credentials Layout - Flexbox Single Row */
.credentials-grid {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: nowrap; /* Prevent wrapping to second row */
  gap: 20px;
  margin-top: 40px;
  max-width: 1400px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  overflow-x: auto; /* Allow horizontal scroll on very small screens if needed */
}

.credential-badge {
  flex: 1; /* Equal width for all badges */
  min-width: 220px; /* Minimum width to prevent squishing */
}
```

---

### Option 3: Reduce Badge Width (If badges are too wide)

If the badges are too wide to fit 5 across, reduce padding and font sizes:

```css
/* Credentials Grid - 5 Column Fit */
.credentials-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
  gap: 20px; /* Reduced from 32px */
  margin-top: 40px;
  max-width: 1400px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
}

/* Reduce Badge Padding for Better Fit */
.credential-badge {
  background: white;
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 32px 20px; /* Reduced horizontal padding from 32px to 20px */
  text-align: center;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  border: 2px solid transparent;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

/* Reduce Font Sizes Slightly */
.badge-title {
  font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
  font-size: 18px; /* Reduced from 22px */
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #1E4D8B;
  margin: 0 0 8px 0;
  line-height: 1.2;
}

.badge-subtitle {
  font-size: 14px; /* Reduced from 16px */
  color: #666;
  margin: 8px 0;
  font-weight: 500;
  line-height: 1.3;
}

.badge-description {
  font-size: 13px; /* Reduced from 14px */
  color: #666;
  line-height: 1.5;
  margin: 12px 0 0 0;
}
```

---

## COMPLETE WORKING CODE

### Full HTML (5 Badges Horizontal)

```html
<!-- Elite Credentials Section -->
<section class="credentials-section">
  <div class="container">

    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="credentials-header">
      <h2 class="credentials-title">Elite Training & Recognition</h2>
      <p class="credentials-subtitle">The Qualifications That Set Dr. Rasouli Apart</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Credentials Grid - ALL 5 IN ONE ROW -->
    <div class="credentials-grid">

      <!-- Badge 1: Castle Connolly -->
      <div class="credential-badge castle-connolly-badge">
        <div class="badge-icon">
          <svg class="achievement-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 2L15.09 8.26L22 9.27L17 14.14L18.18 21.02L12 17.77L5.82 21.02L7 14.14L2 9.27L8.91 8.26L12 2Z" fill="#C9A961" stroke="#C9A961" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="badge-title">Castle Connolly<br>Rising Star</h3>
        <p class="badge-years">2023, 2024, 2025</p>
        <p class="badge-description">Peer-nominated recognition</p>
        <a href="https://www.castleconnolly.com/doctors/profile/1003172974/jonathan-j-rasouli-staten-island-ny" 
           target="_blank" 
           rel="noopener noreferrer" 
           class="badge-link">
          View Profile →
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Badge 2: Dual Fellowship -->
      <div class="credential-badge fellowship-badge">
        <div class="badge-icon">
          <svg class="achievement-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 3L1 9L5 11.18V17.18L12 21L19 17.18V11.18L21 10.09V17H23V9L12 3Z" fill="#1E4D8B" stroke="#1E4D8B" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="badge-title">Dual Fellowship<br>Training</h3>
        <p class="badge-subtitle">Combined Neurosurgery &<br>Orthopaedic Spine Surgery</p>
        <p class="badge-institution">(Cleveland Clinic)</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Badge 3: Board Certified -->
      <div class="credential-badge board-badge">
        <div class="badge-icon">
          <svg class="achievement-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12L3.41 13.41L9 19L21 7L19.59 5.59L9 16.17Z" fill="#28A745" stroke="#28A745" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="badge-title">Board Certified</h3>
        <p class="badge-subtitle">American Board of<br>Neurological Surgery</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Badge 4: Alpha Omega Alpha -->
