### Full CSS (Fixed for 5-Column Layout)

```css
/* Credentials Section Container */
.credentials-section {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F5F8FF 0%, #FFFFFF 100%);
  padding: 80px 20px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.credentials-section::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 4px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1E4D8B, #0066CC, #20B2AA);
}

.container {
  max-width: 1400px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

/* Section Header */
.credentials-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 50px;
}

.credentials-title {
  font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
  font-size: 42px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #1E4D8B;
  margin: 0 0 12px 0;
  letter-spacing: -0.5px;
}

.credentials-subtitle {
  font-size: 20px;
  color: #666;
  margin: 0;
  font-weight: 400;
}

/* ============================================
   FIXED: 5-Column Grid Layout (ALL HORIZONTAL)
   ============================================ */
.credentials-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); /* EXACTLY 5 columns */
  gap: 20px;
  margin-top: 40px;
  max-width: 1400px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
}

/* Individual Credential Badge */
.credential-badge {
  background: white;
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 32px 16px; /* Reduced horizontal padding for better fit */
  text-align: center;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  border: 2px solid transparent;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  min-height: 280px; /* Ensure consistent height */
}

.credential-badge::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 4px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1E4D8B, #0066CC);
  transform: scaleX(0);
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.credential-badge:hover {
  transform: translateY(-8px);
  box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  border-color: #1E4D8B;
}

.credential-badge:hover::before {
  transform: scaleX(1);
}

/* Badge Icon */
.badge-icon {
  width: 70px;
  height: 70px;
  margin: 0 auto 20px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F5F8FF 0%, #E8F0FF 100%);
  border-radius: 50%;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.credential-badge:hover .badge-icon {
  transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E4D8B 0%, #0066CC 100%);
}

.achievement-icon {
  width: 35px;
  height: 35px;
}

.credential-badge:hover .achievement-icon path {
  fill: white;
  stroke: white;
}

/* Badge Text - Optimized for 5-column layout */
.badge-title {
  font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
  font-size: 18px; /* Slightly smaller for better fit */
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #1E4D8B;
  margin: 0 0 8px 0;
  line-height: 1.2;
}

.badge-subtitle {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #666;
  margin: 8px 0;
  font-weight: 500;
  line-height: 1.3;
}

.badge-years {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #FF6B35;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin: 4px 0 10px 0;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

.badge-institution {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: #0066CC;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin: 6px 0 10px 0;
  line-height: 1.3;
}

.badge-description {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: #666;
  line-height: 1.5;
  margin: 10px 0 0 0;
}

/* Castle Connolly Badge Link */
.badge-link {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 12px;
  padding: 8px 16px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C9A961 0%, #DAA520 100%);
  color: white;
  text-decoration: none;
  border-radius: 6px;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 600;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3);
}

.badge-link:hover {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #B89750 0%, #C9A961 100%);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.4);
}

/* Specific Badge Border Colors */
.castle-connolly-badge { border-top: 4px solid #C9A961; }
.fellowship-badge { border-top: 4px solid #1E4D8B; }
.board-badge { border-top: 4px solid #28A745; }
.aoa-badge { border-top: 4px solid #DAA520; }
.faculty-badge { border-top: 4px solid #0066CC; }

/* ============================================
   RESPONSIVE: Keep horizontal on large screens
   ============================================ */

/* Large Desktop (1400px+) - 5 columns */
@media (min-width: 1400px) {
  .credentials-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .credential-badge {
    padding: 36px 20px;
  }
}

/* Desktop (1024px - 1399px) - 5 columns, tighter spacing */
@media (min-width: 1024px) and (max-width: 1399px) {
  .credentials-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .credential-badge {
    padding: 28px 12px;
  }

  .badge-title {
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .badge-subtitle {
    font-size: 13px;
  }
}

/* Tablet (768px - 1023px) - Stack to 3 + 2 rows */
@media (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1023px) {
  .credentials-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }
}

/* Mobile (<768px) - Stack to single column */
@media (max-width: 767px) {
  .credentials-section {
    padding: 60px 15px;
  }

  .credentials-title {
    font-size: 32px;
  }

  .credentials-subtitle {
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .credentials-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .credential-badge {
    padding: 32px 24px;
    min-height: auto;
  }

  .badge-title {
    font-size: 20px;
  }
}
```

---

## KEY CHANGES MADE

### 1. **Fixed Grid Columns**
```css
/* BEFORE (causing wrapping): */
grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));

/* AFTER (forces 5 columns): */
grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
```

### 2. **Reduced Gap Spacing**
```css
gap: 20px; /* Reduced from 32px */
```

### 3. **Reduced Horizontal Padding**
```css
padding: 32px 16px; /* Was 40px 32px */
```

### 4. **Smaller Font Sizes**
```css
.badge-title { font-size: 18px; } /* Was 22px */
.badge-subtitle { font-size: 14px; } /* Was 16px */
.badge-description { font-size: 12px; } /* Was 14px */
```

### 5. **Responsive Breakpoints**
- **1400px+**: 5 columns, full spacing
- **1024-1399px**: 5 columns, tight spacing
- **768-1023px**: 3 columns (allows some wrapping)
- **<768px**: 1 column (mobile stack)

---

## ALTERNATIVE: SCROLL ON SMALLER SCREENS

If you want to keep ALL 5 horizontal even on smaller screens with horizontal scroll:

```css
.credentials-grid {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: nowrap; /* NO wrapping allowed */
  gap: 20px;
  overflow-x: auto; /* Enable horizontal scroll if needed */
  -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch; /* Smooth scroll on mobile */
  padding-bottom: 20px; /* Space for scrollbar */
}

.credential-badge {
  flex: 0 0 250px; /* Fixed width, no shrink, no grow */
  min-width: 250px;
}

/* Hide scrollbar on desktop but keep functionality */
.credentials-grid::-webkit-scrollbar {
  height: 6px;
}

.credentials-grid::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
  background: #f1f1f1;
  border-radius: 10px;
}

.credentials-grid::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
  background: #888;
  border-radius: 10px;
}

.credentials-grid::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
  background: #555;
}
```

---

## TESTING CHECKLIST

After implementing the fix:

- [ ] View on 1920px screen - all 5 badges in one row
- [ ] View on 1440px screen - all 5 badges in one row
- [ ] View on 1024px screen - all 5 badges in one row (tighter)
- [ ] View on tablet (768px) - check if 3+2 layout acceptable
- [ ] View on mobile (375px) - single column stack
- [ ] Check no horizontal scroll on desktop
- [ ] Verify all badges have equal heights
- [ ] Test hover animations still work
- [ ] Verify Castle Connolly link works

---

## QUICK FIX SUMMARY

**The Problem:**
- `repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr))` was causing the 5th badge to wrap

**The Solution:**
- Change to `repeat(5, 1fr)` to force exactly 5 columns
- Reduce padding and gaps to make them fit
- Optimize font sizes for better space usage

**Result:**
- All 5 badges in perfect horizontal alignment
- No badges appearing below
- Clean, professional presentation

---

This fix ensures your credentials section displays all 5 badges in a single horizontal row as intended! 🎯

